Certification Requirements:
---------------------------
1. Safety Certification
   - Laser safety (Class IV laser controls)
   - RF exposure limits (FCC Part 15/18)
   - Magnetic field safety (ICNIRP guidelines)

2. Performance Certification
   - NIST-traceable calibration
   - Independent third-party testing
   - Peer-reviewed publication of results

3. Regulatory Compliance
   - ITAR/EAR compliance for export
   - Dual-use technology controls
   - Environmental regulations

Documentation Required:
----------------------
1. Technical Data Package
2. Test and Evaluation Master Plan
3. Safety Analysis Report
4. Environmental Impact Assessment
5. Quality Management System documentation
